metadata.name: Bubble Beast 4763
metadata.description: 5555 Bubble Beasts on Ethereum - Free Mint - Each Bubble Beast is Completely unique - 4 Billion Years ago the timelines on earth split when a time-traveller from the year 5555 accidentally dropped a bar of soap into the primordial soup. 4 Billion years later - 2nd of July 2022 - The Bubble Beasts are the first species from an alternate universe to make contact with Humans in our Universe via the Ethereum Blockchain.
